Wikipedia

Woerden

A city and municipality in Utrecht province, Netherlands.

endower, reendow, drownee

First attested as wirda sometime after 786. Derived from the dative plural form of Old Dutch uurth (“artificial mound used for habitation”) or Old Frisian uurth (“artifical mound used for habitation”).

IPA(key): /ˈʋuːr.də(n)/

Audio:

Hyphenation: Woer‧den

Rhymes: -uːrdən

Woerden n

A city and municipality of Utrecht, Netherlands.
